Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:37.89,Main Dialogue,Murasaki,0,0,0,,Keby nebol taký hlúpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:39.85,Hamatora Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,Detektívna agentúra Hamatora
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:39.85,Main Dialogue Top,M,0,0,0,,Pravdepodobne odišiel \Nbez zaplatenia jedla.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.15,0:00:41.18,Main Dialogue,Boss,0,0,0,,Nah.
